  "texts": [
    "The regression coefficients are 0.19, which is much lower than the 5% significance level.",
    "As a result, we reject the null hypothesis and accept the alternative hypothesis proposed by the researcher.",
    "Consequently, vigor has a noteworthy and direct influence on organizational performance.",
    "In this context, the regression coefficient signifies that a one standard deviation increase in vigor results in a 0.19 standard deviation improvement in organizational performance, assuming all other variables remain constant.Hypothesis 2: Dedication exerts a statistically significant influence on organizational performance.The importance of the variable has been determined to have a p value of 0.002, along with regression coefficients of 0.12, which is considerably lower than the 5% significance level.",
    "As a result, the null hypothesis is rejected, and the alternative hypothesis, proposed by the researcher, is accepted."
